.TH chocolate\-heretic-setup 6 2017-11-30 "Chocolate Doom 3.1.1"
.SH NAME
chocolate\-heretic-setup \- configuration tool for chocolate\-heretic
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B chocolate\-heretic-setup
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Chocolate Heretic is a modern Heretic engine
designed to behave as similarly to the original Heretic game as is
possible.
.PP
.I chocolate\-heretic-setup
is a tool for configuring Chocolate Heretic.
It provides a menu-based interface for the display, joystick, keyboard,
mouse, sound and compatibility settings.
.PP
.I chocolate\-heretic-setup
can also be used to start and join network games.
.PP
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-config\~ file
Load configuration from the specified file,
instead of
.IR heretic.cfg .
.TP
.BI \-extraconfig\~ file
Load extra configuration from the specified file,
instead of
.IR chocolate\-heretic.cfg .
